IncludeRenderPasses: A list of render passes to include in the capture. Leave empty to export all available passes.
bCaptureFramesInHDR: Whether to capture the frames as HDR textures (*.exr format)
HDRCompressionQuality: Compression Quality for HDR Frames (0 for no compression, 1 for default compression which can be slow)
CaptureGamut: The color gamut to use when storing HDR captured data. The gamut depends on whether the bCaptureFramesInHDR option is enabled.
PostProcessingMaterial: Custom post processing material to use for rendering
